## Summary
This documentation describes the User.com destination integration for Amplitude, which allows sending audience cohorts from Amplitude to User.com for targeted marketing campaigns across multiple channels (email, SMS, push notifications, etc.). The integration requires a paid Amplitude plan and includes steps for setup, configuration, and cohort synchronization.

